<p>Next up: lies about the economy.  Just like I said a week ago when everybody thought Team Romney had forgot about it while going with the Welfare/Medicare lies.  It Economy Lie now.  Then it'll be Obama Lie time.  And when they go through all their lies, they'll start recycling them all together to reinforce the damage from each lie's earlier appearance.</p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:69627275,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3557016&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;13657414&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;disgustedwithitalll&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"><li class="box votes"><div class="label">4 votes</div></li></ul></div><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c69627275" title="Link to this comment">#13</a> - Tue Sep 4, 2012 10:25 AM EDT</span><div class="clearfix"></div><div class="commentcontainer"><span></span></div></div></div></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody " id="c69627429"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:69627429,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;pacokenter&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;pacokenter&quot;}"></div><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="http://pacokenter.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/av/60x60/msnbc.jpg" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="true" /></a><a href="http://pacokenter.newsvine.com/">pacokenter</a></div></div><div id="commentText_69627429" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>Romney dropped the lie to disarm it.   Clinton would have quashed it in his convention speech.  And Obama would have announced: "Republican governors asked for the